description:
With food shortages just around the corner, the world is leaving the cities and moving to the country faster than Gods people. Should we be preparing for the time of Revelation 13:17 when we cant buy or sell? Or will God provide for us? 

This presentation introduces the concepts and events connected with the mark of the beast, including what the mark is, the close of probation, typology of the sieges of Jerusalem, and why we need to leave the cities. MacKenzie Drebit looks at the order of events that happen right at the end of time and the counsel weve been given to prepare for them. 

#amazingdiscoveries #markofthebeast #mackenziedrebit
